The paper focuses on program analysis, which is a subfield of software engineering (cs.SE). It specifically deals with the soundness and precision of program analyzers, which are tools used in programming languages (cs.PL) and security (cs.CR). The paper also uses automated techniques, which fall under the category of automated reasoning and verification (cs.LO) and machine learning (cs.AI).
